Text: Tenorshare Data Recovery Enterprise is a comprehensive data recovery program that support deleted recovery, formatted recovery, partition recovery and Raw recovery. What's more, it supports RAID recovery for RAID 0 and RAID 5. Lost data in RAID 0 and RAID 5 can be deeply scanned and restored immediately. Meanwhile, files and folders in RAID 0 and RAID 5 can be copied to other partitions directly. http://www.any-data-recovery.com/product/datarecoveryenterprise.htm
